list.name: Default
list.comment: Add configurations of the web application, including

task.summary: Initialize the project. Set up maven "pom.xml" file, create the directory structure of the project.
Modify ".gitignore" file to skip the tracking of "workspace.xml" and "task.xml".
Add configurations of the web application, including setting up ViewResolver, ResourceHandler, servlet mapping and ComponentScan.
Update "artifictId", "name" and "url" of the project in "pom.xml".
Create test folder, add some Junit test cases of coap.

Create model classes for "borderRouter", "sensorData" and "sensor" table, declared relationship between each table;
Create database test class "TestHibernate" in "test/com.tw.xg.test.db" package;
Create model classes for JSON, add a test case (test4()) to indicate how to fetch data from database and convert them into JSON.
Declare interfaces and classes in dao and service package.
Update all interfaces and repositories, declare all basic functions we will need in future.
